37 #include <pluginlib/class_loader.hpp>
38 #include <moveit/planning_request_adapter/planning_request_adapter.h>
39 #include <ros/ros.h>
40 #include <memory>
41 
42 int main(int argc, char** argv)
43 {
44  ros::init(argc, argv, "list_planning_adapter_plugins");
45 
46  std::unique_ptr<pluginlib::ClassLoader<planning_request_adapter::PlanningRequestAdapter>> loader;
47  try
48  {
49  loader = std::make_unique<pluginlib::ClassLoader<planning_request_adapter::PlanningRequestAdapter>>(
50  "moveit_core", "planning_request_adapter::PlanningRequestAdapter");
51  }
52  catch (pluginlib::PluginlibException& ex)
53  {
54  std::cout << "Exception while creating class loader " << ex.what() << std::endl;
55  }
56 
57  const std::vector<std::string>& classes = loader->getDeclaredClasses();
58  std::cout << "Available planning request adapter plugins:" << std::endl;
59  for (const std::string& adapter_plugin_name : classes)
60  {
61  std::cout << " \t " << adapter_plugin_name << std::endl;
62  planning_request_adapter::PlanningRequestAdapterConstPtr ad;
63  try
64  {
65  ad = loader->createUniqueInstance(adapter_plugin_name);
66  }
67  catch (pluginlib::PluginlibException& ex)
68  {
69  std::cout << " \t\t Exception while planning adapter plugin '" << adapter_plugin_name << "': " << ex.what()
70  << std::endl;
71  }
72  if (ad)
73  std::cout << " \t\t " << ad->getDescription() << std::endl;
74  std::cout << std::endl << std::endl;
75  }
76 
77  return 0;
78 }
